{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/SHO-steam_description_header-about-EN.png?t=1733953639\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/Back_Ground.gif?t=1733953639\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Decades of rule by the rich have left the world on the brink of collapse. With oppression and corruption running rampant, the people have finally had enough. The Stagers lead the revolution to bring The System down and will stop at nothing to bring justice to this world, facing the most elite agents mustered by the wealthy to defend their ill-gotten gains. Who will you fight for?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Shoot on Sight is a near-future isometric tactical shooter for competitive PVP, cooperative PVE, and solo play, where good tactics matter far more than a big gun. Fight for the future of society on dynamic maps, outsmart your opponents, and remember: Shoot on sight!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/SHO-steam_description_header-features-EN.png?t=1733953639\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/Ability.gif?t=1733953639\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/SHO-steam_description_header-experience-EN.png?t=1733953639\" />The System controls the world, lording over unchecked corruption, extreme inequality, and brutal oppression. Against its elite agents stand the Stagers, rebels fighting for a just world for everyone.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/SHO-steam_description_header-choose-EN.png?t=1733953639\" />Fight the rebels as an elite police agent - or stoke the fires of rebellion as one of twelve distinct characters with unique abilities, unlocks, and backstories to discover.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/SHO-steam_description_header-gear-EN.png?t=1733953639\" />Customize your loadout to fit your playstyle. Bring overwhelming firepower to suppress the enemy. Wade into their ranks with a sledgehammer. Nail them with a well-placed shot through the door just as they're about to breach. The only limit is your imagination.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/SHO-steam_description_header-adapt-EN.png?t=1733953639\" />Walls can be destroyed, windows and doors breached, and almost every object on the map used creatively to gain an edge over your opponent. Wounds leave blood trails, allowing you to stalk your foes - or draw the enemy into a trap, just as they think you are on your last legs.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/SHO-steam_description_header-engage-EN.png?t=1733953639\" />Whether you play on your own, face other players or fight alongside them in 4-player multiplayer modes, you're never alone. As the war for the future of society rages on, you'll be surrounded by computer-controlled friends and foes, keeping you on your toes.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/SHO-steam_description_header-story-EN.png?t=1733953639\" />Whether you win or lose, every match brings you closer to unlocking new weapons, gadgets, attachments, character abilities, and reveals more about the epic conflict at the heart of Shoot on Sight.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1204040/extras/SHO_Track_enemy.gif?t=1733953639\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Five Star Rookie","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1204040/f8ed0cd21a31ac119938711fc20a18b310468047.jpg"},{"name":"Tenacious Leveler","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1204040/f52c4ee00da101a9a51fdd77986dc2baceab2ae5.jpg"},{"name":"Level Twenty Triumph","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1204040/70aa058916ff5f8b393a7a3fafe6464bb069f454.jpg"},{"name":"Thirty Level Titan","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1204040/66bbf3a7eb3eebd3e816577b60d12b05a3658472.jpg"},{"name":"Forty Level Force","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1204040/6ef492aa2f7cbc561e9b6e3ae94126ae91ebb3b7.jpg"},{"name":"Fifty Level Phenom","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1204040/9d8a4b03affb2bb193aa140843271ea85d359bc8.jpg"},{"name":"Sixty Level Sovereign","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1204040/1f289b6f493bd682d7e674fa26b6b17f8de0fbbb.jpg"},{"name":"Seventy Level Supreme","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1204040/a1c48f9604116a7f60af5e9afae8c389d8bb7f4b.jpg"},{"name":"Warrior of Peace","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1204040/e25cd613b91df3bccfb862de9fea1596a91404e4.jpg"},{"name":"Guardian Angel","path":"http